    "In order to validate the model performance on diverse dataset, we used the cardiovascular disease dataset, which is freely available on Kaggle.",
    "This dataset consists of 70,000 instances having 11 independent features.",
    "The computing time column specifically indicates the duration required to train each model once on the entire training dataset per epoch.",
    "As evident from the table, the proposed model exhibits faster training times in comparison to baseline models.",
    "The proposed model also achieves the highest accuracy of 95.2% using the cardiovascular disease dataset, shown in Table 4."
  ]
